attributionInfo.brokerName: Legacy Properties, A Sarah Leonard Company, LLC

data.description: Charming bungalow with a beautiful enclosed porch w original hardwood floors filled with natural light, perfect for relaxing with your morning coffee and a book. Nicely laid out with 1st floor primary bedroom. Also a first floor full bathroom! Separate dining room.The living room is located just off the spacious kitchen. Plenty a cabinets and all new(11/23)SS appliances. The laundry room also located on the first floor with cabinets to for added storage. The mudroom is perfect for all those winter boots and coats! Custom built in cabinets for even more storage.The staircase leads up to the loft area and 2 additional bedrooms with another full bathroom. all rooms including the loft have spacious closets. The loft overlooks the large completely fenced in backyard with a 6 ft cedar fence. Sellers will leave the new pergola 2023 as well as the custom built Island in the kitchen.There's ample room to add a garage if the new homeowner desires. In the highly sought after 303 school district. Newer electrical panel & plumbing,approximately 2013. Furnace and AC 2013  Just blocks away from The St Charles police, plenty of dining options within walking distance as well as a short walk to the Fox River and downtown St Charles.The location can't be beat!!!
